(7, 'Sport.jpg', 'The Exciting World of Sports', 'Welcome to the Sports Wiki, where we explore the exhilarating world of sports and athleticism. Whether you\'re a seasoned athlete, a sports enthusiast, or just curious about various sports, this wiki is your go-to source for information, history, and insights.\n\n### Overview of Sports\n\nSports play a crucial role in human culture, promoting physical fitness, teamwork, and competition. From ancient times to the modern era, sports have evolved into a diverse range of activities, each with its own set of rules, strategies, and dedicated fan base.\n\n### Categories of Sports\n\n1. **Team Sports:**\n   - Examples: Football, Basketball, Soccer\n   - Team sports emphasize collaboration and coordination among players.\n\n2. **Individual Sports:**\n   - Examples: Tennis, Golf, Swimming\n   - Individual sports showcase the skills and abilities of a single athlete.\n\n3. **Extreme Sports:**\n   - Examples: Surfing, Skateboarding, Snowboarding\n   - Extreme sports push the limits of physical and mental endurance.\n\n4. **Racket Sports:**\n   - Examples: Tennis, Badminton, Squash\n   - Racket sports involve the use of a racket to hit a ball or shuttlecock.\n\n### Notable Sports Events\n\n1. **Olympic Games:**\n   - The Olympics, held every four years, bring together athletes from around the world to compete in various sports.\n\n2. **FIFA World Cup:**\n   - The world\'s most-watched sporting event, featuring national teams competing for the prestigious FIFA World Cup.\n\n### How to Get Involved\n\nInterested in trying out a new sport or becoming more active? Here are some steps to get involved:\n\n1. **Explore Local Clubs:**\n   - Many communities have sports clubs where you can join and participate in organized events.\n\n2. **Join Recreational Leagues:**\n   - Recreational leagues offer a friendly environment for people of all skill levels to enjoy sports.\n\n3. **Attend Sporting Events:**\n   - Watch live sports to gain a deeper appreciation for the skills and strategies involved.\n\nConclusion:\nSports are more than just games; they\'re a reflection of our passion, dedication, and pursuit of excellence. Whether you\'re a player or a spectator, the Sports Wiki is your guide to the exciting and diverse world of sports.\n\n[Last Updated: Insert Current Date]', 10, '2024-01-11 14:46:55', NULL, 'verified', 2, 6),
